data.description: Discover this newly renovated ranch-style home that is simply a must-see! Its open floor plan showcases new luxury vinyl plank flooring, complemented by new blinds, new light fixtures, and a fresh coat of paint throughout the entire home. The modern kitchen is a true highlight, boasting elegant granite countertops, a stylish tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient pantry. Step into the inviting living room, with a vaulted ceiling and an electric fireplace. Both full bathrooms have been thoughtfully and beautifully updated. The owner's suite offers the comfort of a generous walk-in closet. Outside, the backyard is fully fenced with the large partially covered patio, allowing for outdoor enjoyment in various weather conditions. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this renovated gem your new home!
